title: Nastia Liukin on Wanting to Quit on the Way to a Gold Medal
description:
Sadie visits with Olympic Gold medalist, Nastia Liukin. Nastia talks about pursuing her dreams without breaking her spirit, life after the Olympics and building an empowering global community for the next generation of women at grandersports.com
